  <summary date="2019-11-19T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Renewable Energy Investment Act of 2019

This bill allows Indian tribal governments and other taxpayers to elect to receive tax excludable payments in lieu of credit amounts attributable to the tax credits for energy property and for electricity produced from certain renewable resources. The payments to such other taxpayers are limited to 85% of the credit amounts.</summary>
